      "text": [
        " خَبَرٍ آخَرَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «غَسْلُ اَلرَّأْسِ بِالْخِطْمِيِّ نُشْرَةٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.292 - In another report, (Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) ) states:\n\"Washing the head with Al-khatmi (a type of herbal shampoo or marshmallow root) is a remedy and a form of refreshment”."
        ]
      }
